HEADWORD: Stickit
<hw>Stick"it</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Stuck; spoiled in
making.</def> <mark>[Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Stickit minister</b></col>, <cd>a candidate for the
clerical office who fails, disqualified by incompetency or
immorality.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stick-lac</ent>⟦br⟧
